  <brief_title>Brief Title : Optimized Endoscopic Submucosal Dissection With Snaring for Colorectal Neoplasm</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Coventional Endoscopic Submucosal Dissection and Optimized Endoscopic Submucosal Dissection With Snaring for Colorectal Neoplasm</official_title>
