  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  colorectal laterally spreading tumor that is more than 20 mm in diameter

          -  other elevated or flat colorectal neoplasm without stalk, that is more than 20 mm in
             diameter

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  colorectal neoplasms that are proven or suspected to be invaded more than submucosal
             invasion

          -  colorectal neoplasms that have severe fibrosis beneath the target lesion

          -  patient's refusal to participate this study

          -  less than 18 years old

          -  subjects who cannot consent voluntarily due to the communication difficulty
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
